      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 17:00:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典首相称德拉吉报告陷入共同债务陷阱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/swedish-pm-says-draghi-report-falls-into-common-debt-trap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典首相乌尔夫·克里斯特松警告称，前欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉提出通过承担联合债务来增强欧盟竞争力，这一策略很危险，可能会分散人们对欧盟所需的更重要改革的注意力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/swedish-pm-says-draghi-report-falls-into-common-debt-trap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 16:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多放宽抵押贷款规定以吸引年轻选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 试图重新赢得年轻加拿大人的认可，他领导的政府将向所有首次购房者和新建住宅的购房者提供 30 年期抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/trudeau-loosens-mortgage-rules-in-bid-to-help-younger-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
