      <title>TikTok 因抗议美国禁令而受到法庭严厉质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从上诉法院小组的质询来看，如果中国所有者不出售这款广受欢迎的社交媒体应用，TikTok 将面临一场艰难的战斗，以避开美国的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将暗杀企图归咎于哈里斯的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gunfire-at-trump-golf-club-latest-jolt-in-chaotic-2024-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普批评总统乔·拜登和民主党总统候选人卡马拉·哈里斯的“极具煽动性的言论”，并称这激发了据称周末在其佛罗里达高尔夫俱乐部发生的一起暗杀事件，而这位共和党候选人则迅速利用这一事件来获取政治利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/gunfire-at-trump-golf-club-latest-jolt-in-chaotic-2024-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
